summary: Hello! I am an automation engineer. I have various experience in preparing PLC, HMI and SCADA software, implementing it and commissioning plants. In my job, I deal with the development of factory automation projects, read process flow diagrams, discuss the automation process with technologists, conduct I/O tests and starting up production lines. In my current job, I have the opportunity to travel and work abroad, which has taught me how to adapt to different environments and get along with different people. I have experience working in the toughest conditions in the far north of Russia when I was working on the starting up of lifting mining machines.
